      "value": "<p>You can stop on a dime when a misstep leaves you open to attack.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Dex 11, Acrobatics 1 rank</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you fail an Acrobatics check to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.3QdtsfnVJsHEdrt0#tumble]{tumble} out of a threatened space, you can choose to stop moving instead of provoking an attack of opportunity. End your movement in your current square and you are @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{flat-footed} until the start of your next turn. If you also have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.K1DuZQv4CKQHxnIk]{Mobility} feat, you are not flat-footed when you stop.</p>"
